trans-unit.source: Provides the options available for resolving types used by the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.View.TypePresenter" />.
trans-unit.target: 提供選項，<see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.View.TypePresenter" /> 可使用這些選項來解析型別。

trans-unit.source: Creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.View.TypeResolvingOptions" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 建立 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.View.TypeResolvingOptions" /> 類別的執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.View.TypeResolvingOptions" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 建立 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.View.TypeResolvingOptions" /> 類別的執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The default types in the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.View.TypePrensenter" /> control.
Creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.View.TypeResolvingOptions" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 建立 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.View.TypeResolvingOptions" /> 類別的執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.View.TypePresenter" /> control should show the type browser directly when a user tries to select a type.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定值，這個值表示使用者嘗試選取型別時，<see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.View.TypePresenter" /> 控制項是否應該直接顯示型別瀏覽器。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.View.TypePrensenter" /> control should show the type browser directly when a user tries to select a type; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果使用者嘗試選取型別時，<see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.View.TypePrensenter" /> 控制項應該直接顯示型別瀏覽器，則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a filter used to filter types in the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.View.TypePrensenter" /> control.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定篩選條件，這個篩選條件可用來篩選 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.View.TypePrensenter" /> 控制項中的型別。
